Wed Jul  8 17:38:43 UTC 2026 - Mia Herkt <mia@0x0.st>

- Update to version 2.1.1:
  * bugfix: IPv6 symmetric difference (--diff) no longer includes
    addresses present in both sets
    gh#firehol/iprange#55
  * tests: added IPv6 multi-input set-operation tests covering
    merge, common, exclude, diff, count-unique and compare
- Changes in 2.1.0:
  * portability: IPv6 now works on 32-bit platforms without native
    __uint128_t, using portable 128-bit arithmetic
    gh#firehol/iprange#45
  * bugfix: DNS resolution prints a failure message when EAI_AGAIN
    retries are exhausted
    gh#firehol/iprange#43
  * tests: endian-neutral binary fixtures and portable uint128
    build coverage
- Drop firehol-dns-handle-EAI_AGAIN.patch

