Wed Apr  8 01:59:06 UTC 2026 - Mia Herkt <mia@0x0.st>

- Add firehol-dns-handle-EAI_AGAIN.patch
  Adds an error message for when the maximum number of retries
  due to temporary name resolution failure is reached.
  Fixes a test case that was failing on OBS due to lack of
  Internet connectivity.
  gh#firehol/iprange#42

